Nerf secret mission!

In part 1 of this inspirational mission with @nerf, we introduce the first two kids in this series. We are able to make a girl named Zahara's dream come true and inspired her to help another kid realize his dream too. You don't want to miss these beautiful moments. Part 2 drops tomorrow.
